By":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:46:07.000Z","msg":"POPO做埋票站part time??"},{"pid":"f9e63942ddcd4c41289327fceceb2ddf218e75a0","tid":1751032,"uid":30491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:46:22.000Z","msg":"屌如果真係被捕人士既票 點解唔光明正大咁樣話比市民知<br />\n做野做到咁係人都知有蠱惑啦 <br />\n真係當香港人戇鳩"},{"pid":"a732dee3f91a7852f0fe96b772c22dbcc90376a2","tid":1751032,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9acb4586f189efadfb6da580d142a4e50dff4be","tid":1751032,"uid":27530,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:30:05.000Z","msg":"立法會文件早有說明:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200410/20/1020270.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F200410%2F20%2F1020270.htm&d=ZQL1o3idxa%2FDGLG1XyUJbw%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=a9d37c5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200410/20/1020270.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會十四題：方便殘疾人士投票的安排<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n<br />\n以下是今日（十月二十日）立法會會議上李華明議員的提問和政制事務局局長林瑞麟的書面答覆：<br />\n<br />\n(省略)<br />\n<br />\n選舉事務處把所有適合殘疾人士使用的「無障礙」投票站指定為特別投票站。根據選舉法例的規定，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>殘疾人士如被編配到一個不適合他們使用的投票站，可在不遲於投票日五日前向選舉事務處要求調配往其所屬選區的特別投票站投票</strong></span>。<br />\n(省略)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:46:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99c8f6113334966c51e607c92ce5140c479766a0","tid":1751032,"uid":106291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:46:36.000Z","msg":"推上國際"},{"pid":"6899f19b00f517949227858f812c708664409568","tid":1751032,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:47:07.000Z","msg":"任何可疑造假 種票 問題票箱<br />\n<br />\n一定要向外媒<br />\n外國議員篤灰大行動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsend埋俾lord 英國上議院有議員來港監票<br />\n<br />\n英國上議院議員來香港監督選舉，有異樣請FB舉報<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1746728\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1746728</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e217c121c038eff99698fd92d58e2e865fc5c100","tid":1751032,"uid":141812,"l