9db10a2fb10495ef5c8b1b231b","tid":1751032,"uid":145021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:49:50.000Z","msg":"4.58 由於在<span style=\"color: red;\">小投票站、特別投票站及專用投票站</span>內不會進行點票，投票站主任(如屬特別投票站則助理投票站主任)<span style=\"color: red;\">會在警務人員的護送下</span>把上文第4.57段所述的加封的投票箱及密封包裹，以及選票結算表<span style=\"color: red;\">送往相關的點票站以點算選票</span>。小投票站及相關的特別投票站的投票箱會送往指定的大投票站，而專用投票站的投票箱會運送到相關的選票分流站或大點票站(視屬何種情況而定)。[《區議會選舉程序規例》第63A(3)及(4)條][2010年1月、2012年9月、2015年9月及2019年9月修訂]<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eac.hk/pdf/distco/2019dc/guideline/ch/dc_ch4.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eac.hk%2Fpdf%2Fdistco%2F2019dc%2Fguideline%2Fch%2Fdc_ch4.pdf&d=ZQL1o3idxa%2FDGLG1XyUJbw%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=e7aeff12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eac.hk/pdf/distco/2019dc/guideline/ch/dc_ch4.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"41a9a1f597772beaae6445969c714b6f7febc218","tid":1751032,"uid":219736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e5a64f0928100c36c4924fce5b91a4f3dcd9b2f","tid":1751032,"uid":126366,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"67a424cd3ce287b6cd3b1fe9bce9712d726872a4","tid":1751032,"uid":219736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a05756f47516d0bfed5a19960bbadcf27350e84","tid":1751032,"uid":71428,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:33:07.000Z","msg":"個指揮官有警察應該要有既態度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:37:42.000Z","msg":"佢哋應份嘅<br />\n平時嗰啲係唔撚正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:42:03.000Z","msg":"屌啦星<br />\n成班嗒晒糖咁<br />\n唔撚記得晒d 721 831 101?<br />\n咁多人中槍受傷<br />\npoly仲有班人未出到黎<br />\n再有一班俾人告緊暴動<br />\n態度好好就拍晒手掌<br />\non撚9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T15:50:15.000Z","msg":"我都睇到呆咗<br />\n我以為撚緊佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898b95e13fda377066145e8dce0babaf7ce7e50e","tid":1751032,"uid":102126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":